{"filter":false,"title":"microsoft-techtalks.php","tooltip":"/digitalsummit/schedule/microsoft-techtalks.php","undoManager":{"mark":28,"position":28,"stack":[[{"start":{"row":277,"column":8},"end":{"row":277,"column":466},"action":"remove","lines":[" It’s a special Wednesday at Digital Summit 2016 and we have packed the day with some very, very special speakers from our partner, Microsoft. Microsoft TechTalks @ Digital Summit 2016 will enable you with the knowledge and skills that you need from DevOps and Cloud including some great keynote sessions from students, professionals and expert. Join us at Digital Summit 2016 and experience the revolution of technology that is happening in Andhra Pradesh. "],"id":2},{"start":{"row":277,"column":8},"end":{"row":277,"column":379},"action":"insert","lines":["It was a special Wednesday at Digital Summit 2016 and we had very special speakers from our partner, Microsoft. Microsoft TechTalks helped us to have some exposure on DevOps and Cloud. There were few keynote sessions from students, professionals and experts as well. The attendees have also experienced the revolution of technology at Digital Summit 2016 Andhra Pradesh. "]}],[{"start":{"row":283,"column":2},"end":{"row":291,"column":8},"action":"remove","lines":["<div class=\"row\">","\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12\">","\t\t\t\t<center>","\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"../registration.php\" >","\t\t\t\t\t\t<button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-info col-sm-12\">Register for the Summit today!</button>","\t\t\t\t\t</a>","\t\t\t\t</center>","\t\t\t</div>","\t\t</div>"],"id":3}],[{"start":{"row":351,"column":31},"end":{"row":353,"column":0},"action":"remove","lines":["","DevOps has become one of the hottest and most talked about paradigm during last few years with the advent and widespread adoption of cloud. Cloud has changed the way applications and environments are provisioned, configured, deployed and developed. The entire application lifecycle process has and is undergoing changes. CIO’s and enterprises are trying to understand how DevOps can help them with being more agile and flexible and the onus is on us to provide the right strategy and implementations to these enterprises on DevOps. DevOps is built on top of few principle and suggests few practices. In this session, we will delve into the details of these principles and practices and see how automation can help us achieve higher agility and flexibility in deploying and configuring environments and applications. The different choices of tools, utilities and services for automating these principles and practices including open source will be discussed in this session. ",""],"id":4},{"start":{"row":351,"column":31},"end":{"row":351,"column":1019},"action":"insert","lines":["DevOps has become one of the hottest and most talked about paradigm during last few years with the advent and widespread adoption of cloud. Cloud has changed the way applications and environments are provisioned, configured, deployed and developed. The entire application lifecycle process has and is undergoing changes. CIO’s and enterprises are trying to understand how DevOps can help them with being more agile and flexible and the onus is on us to provide the right strategy and implementations to these enterprises on DevOps. DevOps is built on top of few principles and suggests few practices. In this session, the speaker explained us about the details of these principles and practices and saw how automation can help us achieve higher agility and flexibility in deploying and configuring environments and applications. The different choices of tools, utilities and services for automating these principles and practices including open source were discussed in the next session. "]}],[{"start":{"row":411,"column":14},"end":{"row":411,"column":368},"action":"remove","lines":["The Internet of Things (IoT) is a key building block for digital business. Every organization wish to be ahead of the curve by the virtue of Product and Process Innovation. Today with the help of IoT and Cloud - one can not only collect the data but can make it intelligent by applying Predictive Analytics and cognitive services for Business innovation."],"id":5},{"start":{"row":411,"column":14},"end":{"row":411,"column":368},"action":"insert","lines":["The Internet of Things (IoT) is a key building block for digital business. Every organization wish to be ahead of the curve by the virtue of Product and Process Innovation. Today with the help of IoT and Cloud - one can not only collect the data but can make it intelligent by applying Predictive Analytics and cognitive services for Business innovation."]}],[{"start":{"row":501,"column":38},"end":{"row":504,"column":13},"action":"remove","lines":["","Containers have been there for long and quite ubiquitous in Linux world. They are part of core Linux kernel. They were adopted but the real adoption started with the advent of Docker. Docker make containers accessible to developers, operations and to the enterprises. So much so, Windows Server 2016 has recently launched and it brings along with it some revolutionary paradigm features that will change the way environments and applications are deployed, managed and operated in windows world. Containers are one among them. Containers have swept the entire industry and is one of the hottest buzzword. Every CIO wants to hear about containers and how they can help in making their applications more agile, flexible and reduce their cost of operations and availability. In this session, we will understand the evolution of Containers. The tools and services available from Service providers, vendors and partners.  Furthermore, how containers are changing the face of DevOps will also discussed as part of this session.  ","</div>","\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"],"id":6},{"start":{"row":501,"column":38},"end":{"row":501,"column":1043},"action":"insert","lines":["Containers have been there for long and quite ubiquitous in Linux world. They are part of core Linux kernel. They were adopted but the real adoption started with the advent of Docker. Docker make containers accessible to developers, operations and to the enterprises. So much so, Windows Server 2016 has recently launched and it brings along with it some revolutionary paradigm features that will change the way environment and applications are deployed, managed and operated in windows world. Containers are one among them. Containers have swept the entire industry and is one of the hottest buzzword. Every CIO wants to hear about containers and how they can help in making their applications more agile, flexible and reduce their cost of operations and availability. In this session, We understood the evolution of Containers. The tools and services available from Service providers, vendors and partners. Furthermore, how containers are changing the face of DevOps were also discussed in this session."]}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":13},"end":{"row":502,"column":14},"action":"insert","lines":[">"],"id":7}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":14},"end":{"row":502,"column":15},"action":"insert","lines":["?"],"id":8}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":14},"end":{"row":502,"column":15},"action":"remove","lines":["?"],"id":9}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":13},"end":{"row":502,"column":14},"action":"remove","lines":[">"],"id":10}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":13},"end":{"row":502,"column":14},"action":"insert","lines":["<"],"id":11}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":14},"end":{"row":502,"column":15},"action":"insert","lines":["/"],"id":12}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":15},"end":{"row":502,"column":16},"action":"insert","lines":["d"],"id":13}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":16},"end":{"row":502,"column":17},"action":"insert","lines":["i"],"id":14}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":17},"end":{"row":502,"column":18},"action":"insert","lines":["v"],"id":15}],[{"start":{"row":502,"column":18},"end":{"row":502,"column":19},"action":"insert","lines":[">"],"id":16}],[{"start":{"row